OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThe chance of a light shower in
OL,6,Fthe north at first. Otherwise it will
OL,7,Fbe dry with some sunshine breaking
OL,8,Fthrough areas of cloud at times.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FIncreasingly cloudy this
OL,11,Fevening with a chance of a few spots
OL,12,Fof light rain. The rest of the night
OL,13,Fwill be mainly dry with clear spells
OL,14,Fand freshening winds.
OL,15,
OL,16,CSaturday:FA rather cloudy morning with
OL,17,Fpatchy light rain spreading southeast.
OL,18,FThen turning drier and brighter for a
OL,19,Ftime into the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
